Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冷至極啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我貼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小律的臉頰好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  看我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…天太冷吉太都彈不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  戴著手套彈就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你彈彈看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  拿不住撥片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚  會鉤在弦上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太讓我失望啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  律
